    "name": "Erv100",
    "profile": "Erv100 is a prolific independent rapper from Alexandria, Virginia, who's making waves with his laid-back vibes and real-life bars.\r\n\r\nWith a hallmark of consistency and longevity across a deep catalog over the last decade, including work with the Jet Life collective (Young Roddy, Fendi P, Cash Fargo, Drupey Beats, Eyezc Haze) and numerous other top-notch underground hip-hop producers (Cedar Law$, Luka Burr, Alex Mack, DianaRO), his sound grows from strength to strength.\r\n\r\nOn this 6-track EP Blaq Medici serves some melancholic and quirky jazz-tinged beats to underlay Erv100's authentic bars about family life (\"Funky Town\", \"Ties\"), being aware of one's environment and associates (\"On The Clock\", \"Vultures\") and the very reason for his artistry (\"Legacy\"). Seasoned LA spitter Vicasso lends a cultured assist on the groovy opener \"Soul Food\".",
